  "prompt": "How early can you check in at the airport for international flight?",
  "response": "The timing for checking in at the airport for an international flight can vary depending on the airline, the airport, and the destination. However, generally, you can check in as early as 3-4 hours before the scheduled departure time. Some airlines may allow you to check in even earlier, especially for long-haul flights. It's always a good idea to check with your specific airline for their recommended check-in times and any additional guidelines they may have. \n\nAdditionally, online check-in options are often available 24-48 hours before the flight, which can save time and streamline the process when you arrive at the airport.",
